parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt does not retract
the seat belt warning light is constantly on
the seat belt buckle is jammed
the seat belt is stuck in the forward or rear position
the seat belt does not tighten when the brakes are applied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt control module can cause the seat belt warning light to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt warning light is constantly on
the seat belt warning beep is constantly on
the seat belt does not retract.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle is jammed
the seat belt buckle does not latch
the seat belt buckle is broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or fails to start
the engine cranks but does not catch
the ignition coil fails
the ignition switch fails
the distributor rotor comes off
the vehicle experiences intermittent stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or experience electrical fires, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences electrical system problems
the headlights or brake lights fail
the trunk fills up with water
there is rust or corrosion
the vehicle emits a burning odor
the headlights flicker or catch fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle slowly loses power
the alternator fails
the battery fails
the vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the starter can cause the vehicle to fail to start, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The starter fails
the vehicle fails to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield seal can cause water to leak into the vehicle, leading to damage to electrical components, corrosion, and safety hazards. In extreme cases, the windshield can shatter, causing injury or accidents.
symptoms: Water leaks into the vehicle through the windshield
water drips into the car during heavy rain
windshield seal fails
windshield glass shatters or explodes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Misaligned windows can cause water to leak into the vehicle, leading to damage to electrical components, corrosion, and safety hazards. Additionally, it can cause difficulties with window operation, leading to frustration and inconvenience.
symptoms: Window does not fit properly in its track
window slides off track
window does not roll up or down smoothly.
